<footer class="border-t border-[#e0d6c8] bg-[#f3ece2] text-brand" role="contentinfo">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <div class="mb-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#d8ccb9] bg-[#f3e8d5] shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.58)]">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="h-5 w-5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#9f6a24" stroke-width="1.4"></circle>
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="9" fill="none" stroke="#9f6a24" stroke-width="1.1" opacity="0.55"></circle>
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="3.4" fill="#1f2a33"></circle>
              <path d="M16 4.5v11.5l7-7" fill="none" stroke="#9f6a24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.2"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <div>
            <div class="font-display text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight">SiteDok</div>
            <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand/46">fra SitedokAI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand/62">
          AI Audit, rooms, workflows og små systemer for små virksomheder der vil være lettere at forstå, lettere at stole på og lettere at drive.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-brand/62">
          Start med AI Audit eller et afgrænset sprint. Byg kun næste lag hvis det faktisk skal bruges.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand/72">Navigation</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p><a href="/#services" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Ydelser</a></p>
          <p><a href="/#rooms" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Rooms</a></p>
          <p><a href="/use-cases" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Use cases</a></p>
          <p><a href="/om" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Metode</a></p>
          <p><a href="/priser" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Forløb</a></p>
          <p><a href="/kontakt" class="text-sm text-brand/62 transition-colors hover:text-accent">Kontakt</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand/72">Kontakt</h3>
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm text-brand/62">
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@sitedokai.com" class="text-accent transition-colors hover:text-brand">info@sitedokai.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-brand/62">Danmark</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-brand/62">Svar inden for 24 timer på hverdage</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-brand/62">AI Audit er stadig entry product.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-[#ddd4c7] pt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-brand/62">&copy; 2026 SitedokAI. Alle rettigheder forbeholdt.</p>
